I don't think the W.W. part referenced is the same thing. The middle rockers
are very difficult to find in the U.S.  I import them from the U.K.  Our
part numbers are 83031 and 83032. They can be found toward the bottom of
this page, along with a diagram:

http://busdepot.com/details/busmetal.jsp

